entertainment games and joy rides, is a huge investment project by
Ddembe Enterprises and the first of its kind in eastern and
central Africa.
</P>
<P>
Entrepreneurship is the "ignition key" in production because it
starts off the process of production, Museveni said, referring to
entrepreneurship as one of the four factors of production
together with land, labor and capital.
</P>
<P>
The president has paid tribute to Karim Hirji of Ddembe
Enterprises and other entrepreneurs in Uganda for the role they
are playing in the rapid growth of the national economy,
according to a press release from the President's Office.
</P>
<P>
Karim Hirji said that his group of companies has been able to
make investment worth more than 100 million U.S. dollars due to
the peace and security prevailing in the country.
</P>
<P>
In 1998-99 financial year, the private investment in Uganda
expanded by 13 percent, and this is proof that the private sector
remains very confident about the prospects of the economy, an
analyst said here Wednesday. 
