<TEXT>
<P>
AMMAN, April 19 (Xinhua) -- Jordanian King Abdullah Bin Hussein
on Wednesday met with Chairman of the U.S. Joint Chiefs of Staff
Henry Shelton, who is in the kingdom to attend an exhibition of
arms, equipments, and technologies for special forces operations in
the capital city Amman.
</P>
<P>
Discussions during the meeting covered relations between Jordan
and the United States, especially in the military field, Jordan's
official news agency reported.
</P>
