 difference in inflation levels between South Africa and its main
trading partners could lead to "systematic and contained
depreciation" of rand, the currency of South Africa.
</P>
<P>
The current exchange rate is "not as bad as people think" and
will stabilize in a short term due to South Africa's free trade
agreement with the European Union, he said. 
