Turkey by forging a new cooperative partnership with Turkey based
on the principles of mutual respect and trust, equality and mutual
benefit, common development and long-term stability.
</P>
<P>
Jiang made the remarks during his talks with Turkish President
Suleyman Demirel.
</P>
<P>
Jiang said that the framework of the new partnership will be
featured with the following characteristics:
</P>
<P>
