percentage points from 8.75 percent to 8.0 percent, and the
secondary overnight rate by 0.50 percentage points from 8.0
percent to 7.5 percent.
</P>
<P>
The central bank also reduced the Lombard rate by 0.75
percentage points from 10.25 percent to 9.50 percent. 
