<HEADLINE> Issue of Angola's Official Newspaper Paralyzed by Mechanical Breakdown </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The mechanical breakdown of the printer is principally
attributed by the source who declined to be identified to the
irregular cuts of electricity on Monday, which have impeded the
press from publishing the Jornal de Angola and the Sports Daily
for two days.
</P>
<P>
