<HEADLINE> Kidnapping Ring Busted (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
So far, police have rescued all 84 victims, seized nine
kidnappers and five salon owners.
</P>
<P>
Since April 1, Chinese police have launched a nationwide hunt
for women and children traffickers, armed with sophisticated means
including DNA-testing kits, and digital and networking systems.
</P>
<P>
The abducted children and their parents will all have blood
samples taken for DNA testing to verify the relationships.
</P>
