"Sangokujin" is an abusive Japanese word that literally means
people from foreign countries and regions.
</P>
<P>
It is a disgrace that "such a mentally deranged politician as
Ishihara stays in the Japanese political circles," the KCNA stated,
adding "Ishihara, who is swimming against the trend of the times,
is bound to face a stern judgment by the unbiased public."
</P>
<P>
Ishihara has drawn an angry chorus of public criticism at home
and abroad, the Asian nations in particular. 
