The Taiwan group has so far set up eight enterprises in the
Chinese mainland in the cities of Shanghai and Guangzhou.
Investment in these eight companies is projected to double as part
of the group's effort to increase its mainland business. The
companies' products are mainly sold in the Chinese mainland.
