<HEADLINE> Model Units, Individuals for Compiling PLA History Awarded </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 19 (Xinhua) -- Some fifty model units and ninety-
eight individuals have recently been praised for their
contributions to the compiling of a series of books on the history
of the People's Liberation Army (PLA).
</P>
<P>
The 250-volume series of books, a huge project approved by the
Central Military Commission, chronicle the PLA history and its
magnificent achievements. The books are a kind of textbooks for
new PLA soldiers in studying the history of the army, the Party
and wars.
</P>
<P>
